    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼与欧盟发生口角，其欧洲议会议员反对冯德莱恩的新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/meloni-eu-spat-on-show-as-her-meps-oppose-new-von-der-leyen-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治亚·梅洛尼领导的布鲁塞尔议会议员投票反对乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩连任欧盟委员会主席，凸显了意大利总理与欧盟机构之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/meloni-eu-spat-on-show-as-her-meps-oppose-new-von-der-leyen-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:08:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国被指囤积天然气供应捷克共和国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-accused-of-hoarding-gas-meant-to-supply-czech-republic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国指责德国在该地区努力寻找俄罗斯天然气替代供应之际，大幅削减出口管道的容量，以囤积天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-accused-of-hoarding-gas-meant-to-supply-czech-republic</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威领导人称美国总统不想放弃乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/norway-s-leader-says-no-us-president-wants-to-abandon-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威首相表示，他不认为美国总统会撤回对乌克兰的支持或放弃北约，因为防御联盟惠及所有成员国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/norway-s-leader-says-no-us-president-wants-to-abandon-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行强烈支持欧盟财政规则的纪律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-strongly-backs-discipline-on-eu-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行坚决支持欧盟推动债务国家的预算政策符合该地区的财政规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-strongly-backs-discipline-on-eu-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 14:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
