      <title>欧洲央行行长 Guindos 希望西班牙在 9 月前任命新行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ecb-s-guindos-hopes-spain-appoints-new-governor-by-september</link>
