    <item>
      <title>乌克兰撤出南部地区战略要地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ukraine-withdraws-from-strategic-position-in-southern-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军队从其坚守数月的第聂伯河以南战略要地撤退，颠覆了其向克里米亚半岛发动反攻、向俄罗斯军队施压的军事目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ukraine-withdraws-from-strategic-position-in-southern-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:10:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲领导人对特朗普在乌克兰问题上的温和立场持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/european-leaders-cast-wary-eye-to-trump-s-tepid-ukraine-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普第二任美国总统的前景，以及这对保卫乌克兰免受俄罗斯侵略意味着什么，悬在大西洋彼岸欧洲领导人重要会议上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/european-leaders-cast-wary-eye-to-trump-s-tepid-ukraine-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
